益，而竊佔他人之不動產者，依前\r\n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。\r\n\r\n附件：","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/110%2c%e8%8b%97%e7%b0%a1%2c969%2c20211130%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,110,苗簡,969,20211130,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"苗簡","JNO":"969","JDATE":"20211130","JTITLE":"竊盜"}